{"tid":1292770,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] 條例未過 已經有公司撤資","createTime":"2019-07-07T12:45:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-07T12:51:47.000Z","uid":237435,"like":32,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1ca8ae6bbacb6c0d72b498135075df8ff4c233b4","tid":1292770,"uid":237435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T12:45:11.000Z","msg":"彭博引述消息人士報道，<span style=\"color: red;\">德意志銀行計劃關閉亞太地區大部分股票相關業務</span>，乃重組計劃的一部分，預計重組計劃最快將今日公布，報道更指，德銀香港總部已有不少員工收拾個人物品準備離開。德銀發言人拒絕回應相關消息。<br />\n<br />\n該消息人士表示，德銀很可能會停止所有股票現金交易及證券研究業務，甚至可能不再包銷亞太地區新股上市，但很大機會保留其保證金貸款業務。亞洲一直是德銀股票發行收入的重點地區之一。<br />\n<br />\n消息人士又透露，多達一半的亞洲股票工作人員將在率先離職，其餘將在今年底前離職，最終的決定將取決於德銀週日的會議，更指香港分行的部份員工已經開始收拾個人物品。德意志銀行股票部主管Peter Selman據報亦會即將離開德銀。<br />\n<br />\n知情人士早前曾表示，監事會正在召開會議討論由首席執行官Christian Sewing提出的計劃，計劃圍繞著急速萎縮的股票交易市場，更有可能會關閉歐洲以外的股票交易業務。"},{"pid":"474a023e10664f524e2d38e38bbfe5050c657f74","tid":1292770,"uid":266592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T12:46:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b17fcea00f6903a1b0fcb2d36ddf102c5bea94d5","tid":1292770,"uid":139916,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T12:47:17.000Z","msg":"好似都想接一排啦喎"},{"pid":"689229992febccc4b8a50cb32a06921fe29dabe6","tid":1292770,"uid":134415,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T12:48:35.000Z","msg":"德銀仲未摺已經係奇蹟"},{"pid":"6aa9ead41771d911760b2ea74fdb56745d58ae3d","tid":1292770,"uid":75804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T12:49:06.000Z","msg":"哩單關咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0a85da7d9b6c634ced591f527a9a73a0d4915aa","tid":1292770,"uid":56698,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T12:50:30.000Z","msg":"德銀垃圾啫 唔關事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"041bb95822454a6c638ab06e375fd547a5176fd3","tid":1292770,"uid":273703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T12:51:04.000Z","msg":"仆街德銀"},{"pid":"029b9f560c521dd78384467b5d7da69ef91c2fd0","tid":1292770,"uid":26333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T12:51:24.000Z","msg":"林鄭又win<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d1e93a32a8c3e3817f942f4729131e2a75be76d","tid":1292770,"uid":96547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T12:51:47.000Z","msg":"關乜事 一早預左要摺架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}